11:49.203 --> 11:53.429
diseases in animals. And very extensive 
laboratory tests are made to diagnose and treat

11:54.491 --> 11:59.799
animals. And in some areas you have embryo 
transplants in cattle and horses, which is a big

12:00.740 --> 12:06.489
business. There they take the embryo from the 
valuable registered animal and transplant it

12:07.250 --> 12:15.582
into the non-registered sheep cow or horse, mare, 
and grow the registered coat. The surgery for

12:23.837 --> 12:28.706
herniated discs in vertebrae of dogs and cats is 
